<article>
    <h2><%= pageTitle %></h2>
    <p>
        Here I want to display three projects in grid format. Each project should have a card that
        contains <b>title, image and brief description</b>
        The card should be clickable, and should navigate to a dynamic route where the user can view
        the project in greater detail.
    </p>

    <section class="flex_container_col">
        <div class="grid_container_col">
            <% for (const project of projects) { %>
            <div class="project_card">
                <h3><%= project.title %></h3>
                <img src="<%=project.image%>" />
                <p><%= project.description %></p>
            </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </section>
</article>
